headline: Seeking Summer 2024 Internship/Coop | MS ITM Data Analytics @ Illinois Tech
summary:
👋 Hello! I'm Ishan Prabhune, a determined and passionate student based in Chicago, Illinois. My journey is marked by my excitement for learning, creating, managing, and delivering innovative solutions to organizational challenges. I thrive on collaborating within dynamic teams and leveraging my exceptional technology skills to drive results in fast-growing and innovative companies.

📚 Currently pursuing a Masters in Information Technology & Management at the Illinois Institute of Technology, I aim to blend my technical prowess with strategic insights to contribute to the digital landscape.

🎓 My educational foundation includes a Bachelor of Engineering in Mechanical Engineering from Savitribai Phule Pune University, along with a Diploma in Mechanical Engineering from Maharashtra State Board of Technical Education.

💼 As a Software Developer, I've honed my skills in a range of technologies, including Flutter, React, and Firebase. At Biencaps Systems Pvt Ltd, I developed cross-platform mobile applications, while at My Future Town Pvt Ltd, I contributed to responsive front-end websites and web apps.

🛠️ I'm proficient in programming languages such as C, Java, Javascript, and Python, and I have hands-on experience with SQL and Data Structures. My language proficiency extends to English, Hindi, and Marathi.

🙌 Beyond work, I'm an advocate for community involvement. I've volunteered at events like Sinhgad Karandak, and I've been an active member of the Mechanical Engineering Students Association and SAE SUPRA.

📩 Feel free to connect with me if you share a passion for technology, innovation, and collaboration. Let's explore how we can make an impact together!
